{"tid":2335962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李偲嫣夫婦曾提交之樣本結果均為陰性 14日短信通知不果 20日離世時呈陽性","createTime":"2020-12-22T09:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T09:34:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a199e0340a7bc2f60eef28900c9145f336c1c867","tid":2335962,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"醫管局：曾短訊通知李偲嫣夫婦檢測結果不果<br />\n<br />\n正義聯盟發起人李偲嫣日前離世，並驗出對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性，她的丈夫其後亦確診。醫管局表示，兩人曾在元朗容鳳書母嬰健康院提交樣本做病毒檢測，結果均為陰性，12月14日曾嘗試以電話短訊通知結果，但並不成功，暫時未知道故障原因，有關部門已跟進。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2371722&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Fbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d58c899a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371722</a>"},{"pid":"c266be191303a5876b57215cd2aca98053cd337a","tid":2335962,"uid":18587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"擺明做樣留樣本留假電話<br />\n<br />\n點知真係有料到"},{"pid":"ac5b8563431893a2662648a16612d427f0b00ca0","tid":2335962,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"首先佢提供左咩樣本"},{"pid":"b292582e2dce33bf9e21f05626b43bcbc32c4dc7","tid":2335962,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"咁係代表係假陰性 定等結果途中先感染？"},{"pid":"4753525929d45fdb5e27120d525f8131bcb697e5","tid":2335962,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"天意"},{"pid":"775e4d0f46bb0aebc496b8de5c0b2cad484e518a","tid":2335962,"uid":118358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"傻西邊識跟指示朝早吐痰呀<br />\n所以即係話，今次係100% 自己囉黎"},{"pid":"c260f8360eed274de36ac487ae857c45a56b1790","tid":2335962,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"唔係驗完就無敵咩<img src=\"/asse